<li id="cite&#95;note-43"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-43">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a href="#CITEREFBennett2021">Bennett 2021</a>, pp.&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.science.org/doi/10.1126/science.abg7586">1528–1531</a></span>
